EMB3531 RK3399 SDK
==================

Components:
  TF-A:    de387341 (main)
  U-Boot:  9f61fd5b (master)
  Kernel:  linux-6.18.24 (vanilla tarball)
  Rootfs:  Debian trixie (arm64)

Build:
  ./sdk.sh all         # Complete build
  ./sdk.sh fetch       # Download sources only
  ./sdk.sh patch       # Apply patches only
  ./sdk.sh build       # Compile all
  ./sdk.sh rootfs      # Build rootfs
  ./sdk.sh image       # Package final .img
  ./sdk.sh status      # Show build state
  ./sdk.sh help        # Full usage

Output:
  workspace/output/emb3531.img

Requirements:
  - aarch64-linux-gnu- cross-compiler
  - qemu-user-static (for rootfs debootstrap)
  - debootstrap, parted, dosfstools, pv
